cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.SY, cs.CY

Reasoning: 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on privacy risks and proposes a privacy-preserving approach for model training. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses model training and inference tasks using user data. 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.SY (Systems and Control) are possible categories as the paper proposes a system where computation is pushed to the data instead of moving data to the cloud. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is also possible as the paper discusses the privacy risks associated with holding and using large collections of personal data in the cloud.
